data.description: This single-story view home sits on a private hillside overlooking the nearby valley and hill tops.  Enter the home through the beautiful leaded glass door to a spacious great room with a dual-sided fireplace, wet bar, and dramatic views to the serene landscape and neighborhood beyond.  The contemporary design, paired with the mid-century modern touches, including an open floor plan, wood beamed vaulted ceiling, large windows and sliders allows an abundance of natural light.  The updated kitchen includes granite countertops, custom backsplash, upgraded cabinetry, a four-burner stovetop with a center grill and pot filler, self-cleaning oven and microwave convection oven, warming drawer, and dishwasher.  The family room offers a fireplace and opens to the kitchen.  There are three spacious bedrooms, including the primary suite, complete with a walk-in closet and a private bathroom with dual vanity, separate tub, and dual head shower.  The other two bedrooms share a bathroom.  The laundry room includes plenty of storage, and there is an additional storage room behind the two-car garage.  Step outside onto the shaded patios, where you can sip your morning coffee or host a gathering under the pergola, surrounded by mature trees that provide privacy and tranquility.  Close to shopping, entertainment and freeways, this unique house will make a stylish home!
